author: Linus Tech Tips
description:
Thanks to AMD as always for being a great partner, sponsoring this video, and supporting us to bring you cool content like this! Show them some love and check them out at https://lmg.gg/f6PMg and stay tuned for the AMD Gaming Room!

Before we start loading gear into our Ultimate Tech House, we’re going to need a house! But not just ANY house. We need a house with room for all our crazy renovation ideas, old enough that we won’t feel bad about ripping up some drywall and new enough that it doesn’t need a bunch of costly repairs. The perfect house will be close to the office so we’re not wasting a lot of time commuting, and won’t cost so much that we can’t afford to make all the upgrades we’ve got planned. But does that perfect house exist? Can we really make it ‘Just Work’ for whoever ends up making our Tech House their Tech Home?

A big thanks to our Realtor, Emma Stewart.  If you need a Realtor in the Vancouver, BC, Canada area, visit her website at https://www.emmastewarthomes.ca
title: I’m Doing Something Crazy - Tech House Episode 1
